WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.650 --> 00:00:06.240
The Great Divide of world history is marked
by the coming of Christ. Prior to His coming,

00:00:06.240 --> 00:00:12.610
civilization was ruled by pocked-marked Caligulas’
who knew only the brute force of cruelty – and

00:00:12.610 --> 00:00:17.949
the drive – not to propagate a race with
a manifest destiny, but a drive, driven by

00:00:17.949 --> 00:00:24.650
self-gratification expressed in the sodomizing
of young boys. But, with the coming of Christ,

00:00:24.650 --> 00:00:31.869
a higher cause, a lofty and noble striving
after the things of the Spirit was set in

00:00:31.869 --> 00:00:38.130
motion. This struggle was highlighted throughout
Christ’s career in His contest with the

00:00:38.130 --> 00:00:45.190
Jewish spirit of His times. That Jewish spirit
was the elevation of man over God and the

00:00:45.190 --> 00:00:50.480
fleshly aim to survive and to rule at the
cost of others. But with the resurrection

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:56.361
of Christ, for 16 centuries hence, Christendom
crushed the Jewish spirit of their times,

00:00:56.361 --> 00:01:02.720
both in the Roman West and the Byzantine East.
With its Cathedrals spiraling toward heaven

00:01:02.720 --> 00:01:09.030
in Leister and in Paris, and its cupola-domed
Churches uniting heaven with earth in Athens

00:01:09.030 --> 00:01:15.540
and in Moscow, the Jewish spirit of their
times lay prostrate in its ghettos and in

00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:22.780
its shtetls. But with the freeing of the Jews
from their hovels into realms of civil authority

00:01:22.780 --> 00:01:29.460
in the 18th Century, our Cathedrals have been
turned into bathhouses and our cupola-domed

00:01:29.460 --> 00:01:37.310
Churches turned into latrines. This diabolical
seed has ever since waged war on the things

00:01:37.310 --> 00:01:41.360
of the Spirit. The very name of Christ, Who
brought us the lofty and the noble, has been

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:48.400
removed from our lips. We celebrate ‘holidays’
now, not sacred rituals which nourish the

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:55.090
soul on the birth of Christ. We date our human
experience with “BCE” and “CE,” bringing

00:01:55.090 --> 00:02:04.040
the lofty ideals of Christ down into base
commonality. Who agitates for this? Jewry!—violently,

00:02:04.040 --> 00:02:12.010
massively, pervasively. A spirit of anti-Christ
has now infested our times. But, a new age

00:02:12.010 --> 00:02:16.930
is upon us. Our youth deserve better than
what the Jewish spirit of our times has given

00:02:16.930 --> 00:02:24.139
them with its Lady Gagas’ of lesbianism,
its Michael Jacksons’ of confused sexuality,

00:02:24.139 --> 00:02:29.029
and having no chance of meaningful marriages
with their jobs being shipped to foreigners,

00:02:29.029 --> 00:02:37.609
cheap labor, overseas. I see Christ coming
on a White Horse, conquering and to conquer!

00:02:37.609 --> 00:02:44.069
I’ll be there - and thousands, millions
of our youth will be with me. We now have

00:02:44.069 --> 00:02:45.500
a cause to fight for!

